OL,7,FDoctors missed critical warning signs
OL,8,Fin the run-up to Thomas Gibson's death
OL,9,Fon the day of his daughter's birth, as
OL,10,FITV News Correspondent Amy Welch
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FA child taking their first wobbly,
OL,14,Ftentative steps should be a milestone
OL,15,Ffor any parent.
OL,17,FHarper's dad has missed out not only
OL,18,Fon this but on meeting his newborn
OL,19,Fdaughter - passing away just hours
OL,20,Fbefore her birth.
