OL,5,Csame day'
OL,7,F"That little girl's got to grow up
OL,8,Fwithout a dad," said Rebecca Moss,
OL,9,FHarper's mum.
OL,11,F"It's just heartbreaking. She should
OL,12,Fhave her dad here."
OL,14,FAn inquest has heard Thomas Gibson had
OL,15,Ftwo heart scans whilst in hospital
OL,16,Fwith a stomach bug.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
