OL,7,FDespite this, doctors failed to detect
OL,8,Fa condition known as "complete heart
OL,9,Fblock". He should have been fitted
OL,10,Fwith a pacemaker. Instead, they sent
OL,11,Fhim home.
OL,13,FOn the morning of his partner's C-
OL,14,Fsection when baby Harper was set to
OL,15,Fenter the world, he suffered a sudden
OL,16,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,18,F"I went over to him and said, 'come
OL,19,Fon, wake up'. He was in his usual
OL,20,Fsleeping position and he just didn't
OL,21,Fmove," Rebecca said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/9
