OL,4,Ccongratulations and condolences on the
OL,5,Csame day'
OL,7,FShe wants to know why her daughter
OL,8,Fmust now grow up without a dad.
OL,10,F"No one should have to have
OL,11,Fcongratulations and condolences on the
OL,12,Fsame day. It's not right, and more
OL,13,Fcare needs to be taken when people
OL,14,Fpresent with symptoms that might be
OL,15,Fmasking something else," she said.
OL,17,FThe inquest concluded it was more
OL,18,Flikely Mr Gibson would have survived
OL,19,Fif his heart scans had been properly
OL,20,Finterpreted.
