OL,7,FThe coroner ordered a Prevention of
OL,8,FFuture Deaths report, which said
OL,9,FWythenshawe Hospital's own
OL,10,Finvestigation was too narrow and
OL,11,Fdidn't do enough to ensure lessons had
OL,12,Fbeen learnt.
OL,14,FWant a quick and expert briefing on
OL,15,Fthe biggest news stories? Listen to
OL,16,Four latest podcasts to find out What
OL,17,FYou Need To Know...
OL,19,FRebecca said outside the inquest: "The
OL,20,Fexpertise that could have saved Tom's
OL,21,Flife was just one phone call away.
