OL,5,Csame day'
OL,7,FClinical Negligence Solicitor,
OL,8,FCharlotte Moore or CL Medilaw: "The
OL,9,Ffamily are satisfied with the
OL,10,Fconclusion that the coroner has
OL,11,Freached, that had the ECGs been
OL,12,Finterpreted correctly, Tom's tragic
OL,13,Fdeath would have been avoided.
OL,15,F"The family are grateful to the
OL,16,Fcoroner for his thorough investigation.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
